Not so #mellowyellow ⚡️💫 @lucyhale in @dolcegabbana for the @instylemagazine #instyleawards last night #fashion #lucyhale #instyle

THIS. Everything about this. The brand, the star, what it stands for, the location (-ahem!!!!) congrats @lucyhale x @hunkemoller on a collection aimed at empowering us and making us feel like the badasses we are born to be. Sensuality and all 🖤🖤 ps I was like 39 weeks pregnant on this set. Lol. Thank you to a very kind and patient crew and to lovely Lucy for sending me home early 🤣🙌 #fashion #collaboration #lingerie #styleandsubstance #lucyhale

latestIgtvVideos.title: LAURA HARRIER x SBJCT x FARFETCH
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I am so proud of this one guys. I really really seek to unify style with substance and this project embodies that. I hope you will check out the work of The Loveland Foundation. Let’s keep paying it forward #whatsyoursbjct. #farfetchworld

latestIgtvVideos.title: ALOHAS STYLE
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I put together some favorite looks and chat about sustainability, style, and substance with one of my fave brands @alohas 🌈👌🏼✔️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy Birthday Jude 💙⭐️🌈
latestIgtvVideos.caption: We had a little mini celebration last night before Jude’s official birthday today as C had to jet to NYC for work last night. So sweet 💙💙💙💙💙💙

latestIgtvVideos.title: RACHEL HILSON x SBJCT
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Our latest @sbjctjournal feature @rachelonacloudyday shines a little light on us in song

latestIgtvVideos.title: Let’s Get Suited
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I met my GIRL @kateupton to talk suiting for spring and how to mix it up to play the part of your most polished, empowered self. Because guys, what we wear should make us FEEL powerful! That’s my two cents, anyways! #NeimanMarcus

latestIgtvVideos.title: The Art of Fashion
latestIgtvVideos.caption: SO WHY is fashion an art? And how? What we wear is the ultimate work of art because the canvas is US. Fashion is an art because it shows the colors of your soul. And what's more moving than that? I  LOVED collaborating with @neimanmarcus for the Art of Fashion.  Let's keep bringing on the (thoughtfully) chic! #NeimanMarcus
